{"tid":1468590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟睇打狗GIF開心返啦大家","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:06:27.000Z","uid":52609,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"232de0b5b4d52bdfdf593c38de381476a4c19b76","tid":1468590,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/XaFhBhp7j4urE0RJA2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FXaFhBhp7j4urE0RJA2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7f7dc027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個月，我地有犯過不少戰術錯誤，但係每次我地都捱得過<br />\n圍稅局 &gt; 道歉<br />\n塞MTR &gt; 不再塞門<br />\n塞紅隧 &gt; 改免費比人過<br />\n<br />\n一定要贏<br />\n721 728 805 811<br />\n大家繼續努力！<br />\n<br />\n記住所有手足共識：<br />\n1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏"},{"pid":"82f406d25b8c114b91c3e7ab086ec361cf31d02d","tid":1468590,"uid":226413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:07.000Z","msg":"即刻笑"},{"pid":"d9835cd1c1afd459f3c1d5c974a3ef118ff950a0","tid":1468590,"uid":204481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"睇佢個撚樣驚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54236be4b1f88f8da9a0046137750318600eb805","tid":1468590,"uid":303458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"好想like<br />\n可惜P牌<br />\n幫手推！"},{"pid":"79871068e3bd2ccf2f36eb1286259653ced7970f","tid":1468590,"uid":52609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/gISUL6NJnRrjApdpIt/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FgISUL6NJnRrjApdpIt%2Fgiphy.gif&h=57db7cbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bed8f3c0f4d56f3ec53a089d7f17ed92ab941ca","tid":14685